WEBVTT

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.976
GB: Followed my sword and swallow.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:36.976
CA: But, surely a true global ethic
is for someone to say,

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.662
"I believe that the life
of every human on the planet

00:09:39.686 --> 00:09:42.663
is worth the same, equal consideration,

00:09:42.687 --> 00:09:45.976
regardless of nationality and religion."

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:48.977
And you have politicians who have --

00:09:49.001 --> 00:09:50.054
you're elected.

00:09:50.078 --> 00:09:51.493
In a way, you can't say that.

00:09:51.517 --> 00:09:53.603
Even if, as a human being,
you believe that,

00:09:53.627 --> 00:09:54.996
you can't say that.

00:09:55.020 --> 00:09:57.372
You're elected for Britain's interests.

00:09:57.396 --> 00:09:59.976
GB: We have a responsibility to protect.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:03.276
I mean look, 1918,
the Treaty of Versailles,